g++ main.cpp
./a.out

Files:

main.cpp : The code for the simulation containing the main function, vehicle classes.
bot_data.txt: This is the file from which main.cpp reads the data about the arena.
First line contains x_length and y_length of the arena
Second line has coordinates for the charging doc
The next x_lenght lines have values of each coordinate
bot_instructions: This is the file from which main.cpp reads instructions to bots
first line contains total number of bots to be created and total number of instructions
next instruction lines contains instructions for each specific bot of form a,b,c,d
a - bot number
b - instruction number
c - x_cord
d - y_cord
